{
  "page": "Amethyst Empress",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Amethyst Empress</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Amethyst_Empress_Oriana_Wiesner.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Amethyst Empress Oriana Wiesner.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/74/Amethyst_Empress_Oriana_Wiesner.jpg/350px-Amethyst_Empress_Oriana_Wiesner.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"461\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/74/Amethyst_Empress_Oriana_Wiesner.jpg/525px-Amethyst_Empress_Oriana_Wiesner.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/74/Amethyst_Empress_Oriana_Wiesner.jpg/700px-Amethyst_Empress_Oriana_Wiesner.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>The Amethyst Empress, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ownix.tumblr.com/\">Oriana Wiesner</a></div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>God-Empress</li><li>Amethyst Empress</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Predecessor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Opal_Emperor\" title=\"Opal Emperor\">Opal Emperor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bloodstone_Emperor\" title=\"Bloodstone Emperor\">Bloodstone Emperor</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nAmethyst Empress</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Great_Empire_of_the_Dawn\" title=\"Great Empire of the Dawn\">Great Empire of the Dawn</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Opal_Emperor\" title=\"Opal Emperor\">Opal Emperor</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Amethyst Empress</b> was the legendary eighth ruler of the mythic <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Empire_of_the_Dawn\" title=\"Great Empire of the Dawn\">Great Empire of the Dawn</a> and one of its last monarchs.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Amethyst_Empress&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>She succeeded her father, the <a href=\"/index.php/Opal_Emperor\" title=\"Opal Emperor\">Opal Emperor</a> but was cast down and slain by her envious younger brother, who crowned himself the <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodstone_Emperor\" title=\"Bloodstone Emperor\">Bloodstone Emperor</a>. According to the annals of the <a href=\"/index.php/Further_East\" title=\"Further East\">Further East</a>, it was the <a href=\"/index.php/Blood_Betrayal\" title=\"Blood Betrayal\">Blood Betrayal</a>, as his usurpation was named, that ushered in the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">Long Night</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.p